{"tid":1361360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【曼城訪港】黃洋：球迷有權利為未來發聲","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:00:27.000Z","uid":32934,"like":115,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a5e682ad32cd985118de5c5317ec19c2c61c35","tid":1361360,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"今晚傑志對曼城在香港大球場的比賽，香港球迷在比賽不同時段作出不用的行動表達他們對「反送中」運動的聲音，包括高唱《Do you hear the people sing》、高舉示威標語、亦有球迷衝入場叫口號。傑志隊長黃洋在賽後表示尊重球迷發表任何意見，正如他在場上會尊重任何對手。而且足球都是生活一部份，有這些事發生很正常，他們的行為亦沒有阻礙場上任何球員，人是有權利為自己的未來發聲。"},{"pid":"879bec55c56e92d5d6150eef5759b394a85c829f","tid":1361360,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:53:28.000Z","msg":"【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d097edd53ff9365246481b3827f9f4ba4e82a7c1","tid":1361360,"uid":2617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔是大陸人黎咩"},{"pid":"63f7b055ee24fac3fea388732221ee3b52fc3869","tid":1361360,"uid":32934,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"d097edd53ff9365246481b3827f9f4ba4e82a7c1","tid":1361360,"uid":2617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唔是大陸人黎咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:55:14.000Z","msg":"呢d係香港人"},{"pid":"59019a0b220202795d1351327de57af45f0a70b4","tid":1361360,"uid":53003,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"睇錯黃洋達<im